parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Corrosion of the air bag sensor can cause the air bags to deploy unexpectedly, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities. Additionally, it can also cause the warning lamps on the instrument panel to illuminate, which can be distracting and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The air bags deploy suddenly
all warning lamps on the instrument panel illuminate
the "Service Engine Soon" light is on
the air bag light is on.
